name: FREAKOLOCO!#113 - Gif Rafa
description:
FREAKOLOCO!#113 - Gif Rafa

Gif Rafa is a good boy. He is working hard to help the animals in FREAKOLAND, making strange GIFs and selling them on the internet. He has already made a pretty good amount of money, but he needs to control himself not to spend it on massages, piercings and toothbrushes.

His favorite song to listen while working is called Biruei Biruei Biruei Now.

Type: Creature / Edition: 6° / Alignment: Neutral Good / Height: 600 cm / Weight: 760 Kg / Strength: 37 / Dexterity: 37 / Constitution: 37 / Intelligence: 34 / Wisdom: 16 / Charisma: 69
